[[File:Eye of newt detail.png|left|100px]]
An '''Eye of newt''' is used in [[Herblore]] to make [[attack potion]]s and [[super attack potion]]s. One eye of newt is needed for the [[Witch's Potion]] and [[Recipe for Disaster]] quests. After completing [[Tower of Life]] it can be used in the [[Creature Creation]] minigame.
